47
00:05:37,403 --> 00:05:44,993
Harkening to these voices, east and west, by early sunrise and by fall of eve, the blacksmith's soul responded, I, I come.

48
00:05:45,053 --> 00:05:47,136
And so Perth went a-wailing,

